textfield.text: The Monster Cup Organizational Committee is honored to request your participation in our unforgettable Trans-California Rally! The Annual Trans-California rally Monster Cup starts on %DATE% at %DAYTIME% from the %SOURCE% warehouse. The rally will pass through all the territory of California and will finish in %DESTINATION% on %DATE1%. The Cup of Monsters Grand Prix winner will receive a monetary prize of %PRIZE% and the title of California champion in high-speed cargo delivery among professional truckers.
